title: Exit Interview: The Eliminated Contestant Breaks Down and Starts Sobbing in Front of Drew Elliott
text:
Shows Exit Interview: The Eliminated Contestant Breaks Down and Starts Sobbing in Front of Drew Elliott "When you see me, because I'm not going to stop, I want you to know that you had something to do with that." by Damian Bellino 9h ago 
Americaâ€™s Next Top Model is down to the final five and had to say goodbye, yet again, to one of their own. Panelist Drew Elliott sat down with the most recently eliminated model to get all the details of her departure and her future. Drew got a much more emotional reaction than he was anticipating.
